@PiiRemover.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000
@ApiKey = demo-api-key-changeme-12345

### OCR — extract text from a document
POST {{PiiRemover.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/ocr/extract
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

Patient: כהן שאול  ID: 205447709  DOB: 30/11/1994  Phone: 058-3245670
--boundary--

###

### Redact — remove PII from a document
POST {{PiiRemover.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/redact/redact
X-Api-Key: {{ApiKey}}
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

Patient: כהן שאול  ID: 205447709  DOB: 30/11/1994  Phone: 058-3245670  Email: shaul@mail.co.il
--boundary--

###

### Hash a value (no auth required)
POST {{PiiRemover.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/util/hash
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "value": "2026"
}

###
